column5: Looks like I have a happy little helper down at the farm.  She bugs me to let her come along and help.  Gotta love it
Looks great Bruce  nice to have help! I have small garden and love to grow  egggies, but I have voles that eat whatever I plant! One of my grands loves eating my basil.
Welll I just feed the voles, no vet bills. Two years ago I lost  $24  worth of plants in three days. I did got  one three weeks ago. May he RIP.
